Package agile.feature

Class Feature

  • java.lang.Object
    • agile.feature.AgileObject
      • agile.feature.Feature
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CapacityFeature, ProgramFeature

    public abstract class Feature
extends AgileObject
    The Feature class represents a subset of work in an agile planning environment. A feature instance is identified by a unique feature key. Two features with matching feature keys are considered to be the same feature.
